quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,"Hargiz nahin,kasam hai Chand ki"
  74,33,Aur Raat ki jabke woh palat-ti hai
  74,34,Aur subah ki jabke woh roshan hoti hai
  74,35,Yeh dozakh bhi badi cheezon mein se ek hai
  74,36,Insano ke liye darawa
  74,37,Tum mein se har us shaks ke liye darawa jo aagey badhna chahey ya pichey reh jana chahey
  74,38,"Har mutanaffis, apne kasb ke badle rehan hai (hostage to one’s deeds)"
  74,39,Dayein bazu walon ke siwa
  74,40,"Jo jannaton mein hongey, wahan woh"
  74,41,Mujrimon se puchenge
  74,42,Tumhein kya cheez dozakh mein le gayi
  74,43,woh kahenge “hum namaz padne walon mein se na thay
  74,44,Aur miskeen ko khana nahin khilate thay
  74,45,Aur haqq ke khilaf batein banane walon ke saath milkar hum bhi batein banane lagte thay
  74,46,Aur roz-e-jaza ko jhoot karar dete thay
  74,47,Yahan tak ke humein us yaqeeni cheez se saabqa pesh aa gaya”
  74,48,Us waqt sifarish karne walon ki sifarish unke kisi kaam na ayegi
  74,49,Aakhir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh is nasihat se mooh moad rahey hain
  74,50,Goya yeh jungli gadhey hain
  74,51,Jo Sher se darr kar bhaag padey hain
  74,52,Balke inmein se to har ek yeh chahta hai ke uske naam khule khat (scroll/scripture) bhejey jaye
  74,53,"Hargiz nahin, Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh aakhirat ka khauf nahin rakhtey"
  74,54,"Hargiz nahin,yeh to ek nasihat hai"
  74,55,Ab jiska jee chahey issey sabaq hasil karle
  74,56,Aur yeh koi sabaq hasil na karengey illa yeh ke Allah hi aisa chahey woh iska haqdar hai ke ussey taqwa kiya jaye aur woh iska ehal hai ke (taqwa karne walon ko) baksh de